videos.description: Ethan Happ grabs the rebound and takes it himself for a layup.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Happ goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Khalil Iverson sends home a two-handed slam off a bounce pass from Ethan Happ.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's ball movement leads to Iverson dunk

videos.description: Ethan Happ hits Khalil Iverson with a backdoor pass for another two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Happ finds Iverson again for dunk

videos.description: Aaron Holiday works his way into the paint and makes a layup just before the buzzer to bring the Bruins within seven at the half.
videos.headline: UCLA's Holiday beats halftime buzzer

videos.description: Jaylen Hands makes a driving layup to give UCLA the lead over Wisconsin. Hands comes up hobbling with a lower-leg injury after the play, but stays in the game.
videos.headline: Hands lands awkwardly after layup

videos.description: D'Mitrik Trice catches defenders watching on the pick-and-roll and feeds Ethan Happ, who throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Happ rolls to the rim for thunderous dunk

videos.description: Aaron Holiday knocks down a 3-pointer with under a minute remaining to give UCLA a 70-67 lead.
videos.headline: UCLA's Holiday rattles home 3-pointer

videos.description: Aaron Holiday evades Wisconsin defenders on the way to a basket as UCLA escapes with a 72-70 win over Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Holiday makes game-winning layup
